        THE_ELDER_S_A_WARRIOR_THE_YOUNGER_A                                     = 7616,  -- The elder's a warrior, the younger a thinker, and neither bows to the other. The two knightly orders' loyalties are split between them...
        WITH_SUCH_INTRIGUE_INSIDE_OUR_WALLS_BEASTMEN_ROAM                       = 7617,  -- With such intrigue inside our walls, beastmen roam the countryside. And there's precious little we can do about it!
        A_PICKPOCKET_EH_WELL_I_CAN_SEE_A                                        = 7618,  -- A pickpocket, eh? Well, I can see a lot from up here, but the only shady character I've noticed is that bloke by the cargo room, there.
        PAY_GIL_AND_LEAVE_SAN_D_ORIA_YES                                        = 7619,  -- Pay # gil and leave San d'Oria? Yes. No.
        TICKET_PLEASE                                                           = 7620,  -- Ticket, please.
        I_M_SORRY_BUT_IS_REQUIRED_TO_GO                                         = 7621,  -- I'm sorry, but % is required to go beyond this door.
        I_M_TERRIBLY_SORRY_BUT_YOU_DON_T                                        = 7622,  -- I'm terribly sorry, but you don't have enough money. You will need # gil. Please come again.
        THAT_S_GIL_PLEASE_GO_AHEAD                                              = 7623,  -- That's # gil. Please go ahead.
        THIS_IS_SAN_D_ORIA_CUSTOMS_WE_MUST                                      = 7624,  -- This is San d'Oria Customs. We must check the belongings of all who enter our kingdom. Thank you.
        CARRIERS_OF_RESTRICTED_ITEMS_MUST_SELL_THEM_AT                          = 7625,  -- Carriers of restricted items must sell them at the stall over there, or dispose of them before exiting. Thank you.
        PLEASE_BEWARE_THAT_SMUGGLING_CONTRABAND_INTO_SAN_D                      = 7626,  -- Please beware that smuggling contraband into San d'Oria is a serious offense. Thank you.
        ALL_PASSENGERS_PLEASE_PRESENT_YOUR_AT_THE_DOOR                          = 7627,  -- All passengers, please present your % at the door.
        THIS_IS_THE_EXIT_PLEASE_FIND_THE_ENTRANCE                               = 7628,  -- This is the exit. Please find the entrance to the air travel agency to your left.
        WELCOME_TO_THE_KINGDOM_OF_SAN_D_ORIA                                    = 7629,  -- Welcome to the Kingdom of San d'Oria. Before entering the city, please see the customs officer at the counter.
        IF_YOU_WOULD_RATHER_BOARD_THE_AIRSHIP_PLEASE                            = 7630,  -- If you would rather board the airship, please return to the docks and await the next flight.
        WELCOME_TO_THE_KINGDOM_OF_SAN_D_ORIA_2                                  = 7631,  -- Welcome to the Kingdom of San d'Oria. The door ahead will take you into the city.
        PLEASE_BE_ADVISED_THAT_IF_YOU_WISH_TO                                   = 7632,  -- Please be advised that if you wish to board an airship after exiting, you will have to pay your fare again.
        ENTER_THE_CITY_RIGHT_AWAY_NOT_NOW                                       = 7633,  -- Enter the city? Right away. Not now.
        WELCOME_TO_THE_AIR_TRAVEL_AGENCY_PASSENGERS_WISHING                     = 7634,  -- Welcome to the air travel agency. Passengers wishing to embark may purchase tickets here.
        ID_1_GMRS7SP_E7_M_VF_HH_7B                                              = 7635,  -- 1?gMrs7sP|E7%%M%vF Hh\7B
        THIS_IS_THE_AUCTION_HOUSE                                               = 7636,  -- This is the auction house.
        A_PICKPOCKET_NO_ONE_LIKE_THAT_AROUND_HERE                               = 7637,  -- A pickpocket? No one like that around here.
        WELCOME_TO_THE_AUCTION_HOUSE_IF_YOU_VE                                  = 7638,  -- Welcome to the auction house. If you've something to auction, see one of the service windows on either side.
        THIS_IS_THE_AUCTION_HOUSE_SELLERS_SET_A                                 = 7639,  -- This is the auction house. Sellers set a minimum price for their goods, and buyers make bids on the items they want.
        IF_THE_BUYER_S_BID_IS_ABOVE_THE                                         = 7640,  -- If the buyer's bid is above the seller's asking price, the deal goes through!
        HAVE_I_SEEN_ANYONE_SUSPICIOUS_NO_NOT_AROUND                             = 7641,  -- Have I seen anyone suspicious? No, not around here. Sorry!
        THE_SHADOW_LORD_TURNED_THE_BEASTMEN_INTO_FIERCE                         = 7642,  -- The Shadow Lord turned the beastmen into fierce opponents in the Great War twenty years ago.
        ALAS_WHAT_A_TERRIBLE_SIGHT_THEY_WERE_I                                  = 7643,  -- Alas, what a terrible sight they were! I still shiver just thinking of them!
        IF_HEROES_HADN_T_COME_FORTH_TO_STOP                                     = 7644,  -- If heroes hadn't come forth to stop the Shadow Lord...who knows what would have become of this world!
        BEYOND_LIES_THE_RESIDENTIAL_AREA                                        = 7645,  -- Beyond lies the residential area.
        THE_AIRSHIP_DOCKS_ARE_DOWN_THIS_CORRIDOR_NOT                            = 7646,  -- The airship docks are down this corridor. Not that they'd let a two-gil guard and a starry-eyed adventurer on one of those airships, eh?
        BUT_THEY_CANNOT_HOLD_US_BACK_WORK_HARD                                  = 7647,  -- But they cannot hold us back! Work hard, and our day will come. We shall ride that airship together!
        A_PICKPOCKET_NO_NOT_ROUND_HERE                                          = 7648,  -- A pickpocket? No, not round here.
        THIS_CORRIDOR_LEADS_TO_AN_AUCTION_HOUSE_PRINCE                          = 7649,  -- This corridor leads to an auction house. Prince Pieuje ordered their construction. But if you ask me, such places do not become our grand city.
        A_PROUD_ELVAAN_WOULD_NOT_PEDDLE_WARES_LIKE                              = 7650,  -- A proud Elvaan would not peddle wares like some Hume merchant... How times have changed!
        BUT_IF_YOU_MUST_GO_THE_FAR_CORRIDOR                                     = 7651,  -- But if you must go, the far corridor there leads to the residential area. After all, even knights must rest!
        HMM_SOMEONE_SUSPICIOUS_NOW_THAT_YOU_MENTION_IT                          = 7652,  -- Hmm? Someone suspicious? Now that you mention it, I did see a woman dart up the western stair, that way.
        BELOW_THESE_STAIRS_LIES_THE_AUCTION_HOUSE_SOME                          = 7653,  -- Below these stairs lies the auction house. Some may grumble about proud San d'Orians reduced to squabbling merchants, but I care not.
        IN_FACT_I_AGREE_WITH_PRINCE_PIEUJE_THE                                  = 7654,  -- In fact, I agree with Prince Pieuje. The Kingdom must welcome change, before the rest of the world passes her by.
        A_PICKPOCKET_NOW_THERE_S_A_SCOUNDREL_UNWORTHY                           = 7655,  -- A pickpocket? Now there's a scoundrel unworthy of San d'Oria! It wasn't an Elvaan, was it?
        THIS_PASSAGE_LEADS_TO_THE_AIRSHIP_DOCKS_THERE                           = 7656,  -- This passage leads to the airship docks. There's a magic shop if you take the corridor on the right there.
        MAGIC_IS_THE_SPECIALTY_OF_THE_FEDERATION_OF                             = 7657,  -- Magic is the specialty of the Federation of Windurst, of course. We have some, but for true sorcery you have to search there.
        AYE_PICKPOCKETS_WILL_GET_YOU_IF_YOU_DON                                 = 7658,  -- Aye, pickpockets will get you if you don't watch yourself.
        AHEAD_LIES_THE_PORT_WHERE_AIRSHIPS_ARE_LADEN                            = 7659,  -- Ahead lies the port, where airships are laden with goods for Jeuno. You'll find an auction house and the residential area, too.
        THE_BRUGAIRE_CONSORTIUM_OWNS_THE_CARGO_ROOMS_THERE                      = 7660,  -- The Brugaire Consortium owns the cargo rooms there. They're on good terms with Monarlais Halver and the papsque, I hear.
        A_PICKPOCKET_THINGS_SURE_HAVE_GOTTEN_ROUGH_AROUND                       = 7661,  -- A pickpocket? Things sure have gotten rough around here. You watch yourself.
        TAKE_THIS_CORRIDOR_IF_YOU_RE_HEADING_TO                                 = 7662,  -- Take this corridor if you're heading to Northern San d'Oria or Southern San d'Oria.
        SHE_WENT_DOWN_THIS_CORRIDOR_GET_THAT_RAPSCALLION                        = 7663,  -- She went down this corridor! Get that rapscallion, quick!
        TAKE_A_LEFT_TO_FIND_THE_MAGIC_SHOP                                      = 7664,  -- Take a left to find the magic shop. Keep going straight for the residential area. Oh, and take care not to upset Regine; she's scary when she's mad!
        HEY_THAT_PICKPOCKET_JUST_RAN_THAT_WAY_GET                               = 7665,  -- Hey, that pickpocket just ran that way! Get after her, quick!
        UP_AHEAD_ARE_THE_AIRSHIP_DOCKS_THE_GRAND                                = 7666,  -- Up ahead are the airship docks. The Grand Duchy of Jeuno runs all the airships, you know.
        ONLY_THOSE_OF_GOOD_STANDING_OR_DEEP_POCKETS                             = 7667,  -- Only those of good standing, or deep pockets, are allowed onboard. I can't see why you'd want to go there.
        THE_RESIDENTIAL_AREA_IS_UP_THESE_STAIRS_IF                              = 7668,  -- The residential area is up these stairs. If you ask me, San d'Orians must cast aside the trappings of wealth.
        IT_S_NOT_KNIGHTLY_TO_SIT_ON_CUSHIONED                                   = 7669,  -- It's not knightly to sit on cushioned couches in gilt halls! No, we should sleep with the grass as our pillow, the dew our morning gown.
        YET_OUR_KINGDOM_SUPPLIES_THOSE_FOOL_MOG_HOUSES                          = 7670,  -- Yet our kingdom supplies those fool Mog Houses for all! Moogles, or whatever they call those demons, have no place in a proper San d'Orian home.
        I_D_LIKE_TO_JUST_TO_TAKE_A                                              = 7671,  -- I'd like to just to take a moogle and-- Ah, pardon me, I was lost in thought. No, I haven't seen anyone suspicious.
        THE_AUCTION_HOUSE_IS_DOWN_THIS_CORRIDOR                                 = 7672,  -- The auction house is down this corridor.
        THE_AIRPORT_DOCKS_ARE_AT_THE_END_OF                                     = 7673,  -- The airport docks are at the end of this corridor.
