        M_G2N_P_3_L_B                                                           = 7827,  -- #m)g2N%-`p(3_=L>B
        BL_P_D_EL_MEQ_IF_I_S3J                                                  = 7828,  -- bl=?p&"D"= %EL$MEQ%iF$I%s3j=%$b>B
        I_VE_BEEN_HEARING_TROUBLING_THINGS_LATELY_THE                           = 7829,  -- I've been hearing troubling things, lately. The beastmen are rising again, they say.
        IT_S_NOT_TRUE_IS_IT_I_COULDN                                            = 7830,  -- It's not true, is it? I couldn't bear another war like twenty years ago. Those were dark times for all of Vana'diel.
        I_M_SCARED_I_M_VERY_SCARED_MY                                           = 7831,  -- I'm scared... I'm very scared. My husband, my children, my friends...all the people I've come to know these twenty years. I will not lose them to another war!
        HEARD_THE_WHISPERS_HAVE_YOU_THE_BEASTMEN_HAVE                           = 7832,  -- Heard the whispers, have you? The beastmen have a new leader. War is preparing!
        AH_BUT_ANY_HORDE_OF_BEASTMEN_WILL_BREAK                                 = 7833,  -- Ah, but any horde of beastmen will break upon these walls like water. Long live King Destin!
        LONG_LIVE_KING_DESTIN_HUH_PICKPOCKETS_CAN_T                             = 7834,  -- Long live King Destin! Huh? Pickpockets? Can't you see I'm in the middle of something here?
        ORCS_HAVE_BEEN_HARASSING_US_EVER_SINCE_THEY                             = 7835,  -- Orcs have been harassing us ever since they took West Ronfaure. Confound those beastmen!
        BUT_WHERE_ARE_THE_KNIGHTS_THEY_SHOULD_HAVE                              = 7836,  -- But where are the knights? They should have stomped their camps flat months ago, just like in the Great War.
        CONFOUND_THEM_GIVE_ME_A_SWORD_AND_EH                                    = 7837,  -- Confound them! Give me a sword and... Eh? A pickpocket? Do I look like I hang out with that sort?
        ID_11M_V_A_G_3F1_VS_B                                                   = 7838,  -- 11M'|V~>%A=g%3F1$Vs/B
        WELL_WELL_A_NEW_RECRUIT_I_WAS_ONCE                                      = 7839,  -- Well, well... A new recruit! I was once an adventurer myself. Mind you, that was a long time ago...
        AYE_THERE_HASN_T_BEEN_A_WAR_SINCE                                       = 7840,  -- Aye, there hasn't been a war since the beastmen rose twenty years ago. I tried to settle down, and sold off my armor for some city clothes.
        BUT_THIS_SON_OF_ADVENTURERS_COULDN_T_GIVE                               = 7841,  -- But this son of adventurers couldn't give up his heritage for steady work. Not for lack of trying, mind you!
        ALWAYS_GOT_INTO_FIGHTS_WITH_SUPERIORS_OR_QUIT                           = 7842,  -- Always got into fights with superiors, or quit at the first hint of boredom. Come to think of it, I've gotten nowhere, have I?
        I_WON_T_COMPLAIN_BUT_SAN_D_ORIA                                         = 7843,  -- I won't complain, but San d'Oria's days of glory are gone forever.
        OUR_DAYS_OF_GLORY_ARE_GONE_FOREVER                                      = 7844,  -- Our days of glory are gone forever.
        A_TENSHODO_MEMBER_ARE_YOU_SAY_IF_YOU                                    = 7845,  -- A Tenshodo member, are you? Say, if you're interested, I've got something that needs doing. Might be worth a listen, at least.
        HOW_ABOUT_IT_HEAR_WHAT_HE_HAS_TO                                        = 7846,  -- How about it? Hear what he has to say. Not now.
        I_SEE_I_SEE_WELL_TO_EACH_HIS                                            = 7847,  -- I see, I see. Well, to each his/her] own. You come back if you change your mind.
        THAT_S_THE_SPIRIT_NOW_TO_BUSINESS_I                                     = 7848,  -- That's the spirit! Now to business. I've got something I want you to take to the Tenshodo in Jeuno.
        THERE_S_A_BIT_OF_A_STORY_BEHIND                                         = 7849,  -- There's a bit of a story behind this one... But nothing that need concern you! You just take it to the Tenshodo for me.
        I_D_BRING_IT_BY_FOOT_IF_I                                               = 7850,  -- I'd bring it by foot, if I wasn't so sure it'd get broken. Airship's the way to go... But then there's customs to deal with.
        YOU_LL_GET_IT_THROUGH_WON_T_YOU                                         = 7851,  -- You'll get it through, won't you? If they catch you, they'll only confiscate the goods and keep you from flying for a while. No worries! I'll pay good, I will.
        ALL_YOU_HAVE_TO_DO_IS_DELIVER_SOME                                      = 7852,  -- All you have to do is deliver some goods by airship to the Tenshodo in Jeuno.
        HOW_ABOUT_IT_LET_S_DO_IT_I                                              = 7853,  -- How about it? Let's do it. I don't think so.
        THAT_S_WHAT_I_LIKE_TO_HEAR_JUST                                         = 7854,  -- That's what I like to hear! Just hop on the airship to Jeuno, and make sure this gets to Yin Pocanakhu at the Tenshodo there.
        AND_IT_MIGHT_BE_BEST_TO_WAIT_UNTIL                                      = 7855,  -- And it might be best to wait until nightfall.
        YOU_RE_DOING_YOURSELF_A_DISSERVICE_NOT_TAKING                           = 7856,  -- You're doing yourself a disservice, not taking this job, you know. Come back if you change your mind.
        JUST_MAKE_THE_DELIVERY_TO_YIN_POCANAKHU_AT                              = 7857,  -- Just make the delivery to Yin Pocanakhu at the Tenshodo in Jeuno. Don't worry! If you're caught, they'll just suspend your Jeuno flight privileges a short while.
        BUT_IF_YOU_RE_STILL_A_TOUCH_WORRIED                                     = 7858,  -- But if you're still a touch worried, you might consider waiting until nightfall.
        YOU_MADE_IT_YOU_RE_A_LUCKY_ONE                                          = 7859,  -- You made it! You're a lucky one, then; they always seem to catch me. Oh, and your money, as promised!
        EH_THEY_CAUGHT_YOU_AH_JUST_A_STRIPE                                     = 7860,  -- Eh, they caught you? Ah, just a stripe of bad luck, that's all. This business is like rolling dice.
        SORRY_TO_PUT_YOU_IN_A_FIX_EH                                            = 7861,  -- Sorry to put you in a fix, eh? But don't let it get you down! There's always next time!
        WHAT_DAMAGED_IT_DID_YOU_PAY_ATTENTION_WHEN                              = 7862,  -- What? Damaged it, did you? Pay attention when I talk to you! Take it on the airship next time!
        I_LL_ASK_YOU_AGAIN_ONCE_YOU_GET                                         = 7863,  -- I'll ask you again once you get your flight privileges back in Jeuno. Best lay low for now.
        WHAT_S_THIS_A_MAGIC_SHOP_HMM_I                                          = 7864,  -- What's this? A magic shop? Hmm...I could use a new line of work, and magic just might be the ticket!
        I_HEARD_THAT_THE_BRUGAIRE_CONSORTIUM_THAT_RUNS                          = 7865,  -- I heard that the Brugaire Consortium that runs these warehouses is looking for workers.
        THEY_RE_ONE_OF_SAN_D_ORIA_S                                             = 7866,  -- They're one of San d'Oria's biggest trading companies...but I hear they're a little rough with their staff.
        AND_PEOPLE_SAY_THEY_SMUGGL_AHEM_WOULDN_T                                = 7867,  -- And people say they smuggl--ahem! Wouldn't want a prospective employer to hear me saying that, now would I!
        WHAT_A_PICKPOCKET_HEY_I_MAY_BE_A                                        = 7868,  -- What? A pickpocket? Hey! I may be a loafer, but I'm no thief!
        ARE_YOU_CONFIDENT_IN_YOUR_FAITH_SOMEWHERE_OUT                           = 7869,  -- Are you confident in your faith? Somewhere out there lies the gate to eternal paradise.
        WE_ARE_CHILDREN_OF_THE_GODDESS_OF_THE                                   = 7870,  -- We are children of the Goddess of the Dawn. She is the mother of all living things, and Vana'diel is her cradle.
        I_AM_TEILSA_ONE_OF_THE_FAITHFUL_EVER                                    = 7871,  -- I am Teilsa, one of the faithful. Ever do I seek the way to Paradise.
        IF_YOU_LOSE_YOUR_WAY_CHOOSE_MAP_FROM                                    = 7872,  -- If you lose your way, choose Map from your main menu. Here, let me give you this in exchange for your %.
        BLESSED_ARE_THE_BELIEVERS_ALWAYS_ARE_WE_BATHED                          = 7873,  -- Blessed are the believers. Always are we bathed in the light of the Goddess, and soothing is the sound of her song.
        BLESSED_ARE_THE_BELIEVERS_FOR_SPARED_ARE_WE                             = 7874,  -- Blessed are the believers, for spared are we her pain and sorrow. Her cold blade will never touch us.
        SOON_YOU_WILL_SEE_SHADOWS_OF_CHAOS_WILL                                 = 7875,  -- Soon you will see. Shadows of chaos will fall upon Vana'diel, and herald the coming of Crystal Warriors.
        THE_GODDESS_OF_THE_DAWN_SPOKE_HE_WHO                                    = 7876,  -- The Goddess of the Dawn spoke: He who fails to question his faith is blind. A believer without doubt will turn gold to lead.
        I_CAN_ONLY_LIGHT_THY_CANDLE_THOU_MUST                                   = 7877,  -- I can only light thy candle; thou must carry thy own.
        I_CANNOT_LEAD_THEE_FOR_THY_PATH_IS                                      = 7878,  -- I cannot lead thee, for thy path is thine alone. Let the light of thy candle guide thee.
        HE_WHO_FINDS_ME_AT_THE_JOURNEY_S                                        = 7879,  -- He who finds me at the journey's end... That is all. No one knows what follows.
        BUT_THE_DAY_WILL_COME_WHEN_ALL_IS                                       = 7880,  -- But the day will come when all is revealed.
        BEHOLD_SAN_D_ORIA_CITY_OF_LEGENDS_I                                     = 7881,  -- Behold San d'Oria, city of legends! I've always wanted to come here and join a proud order of knights.
        THEY_DON_T_LET_RAW_RECRUITS_INTO_THE                                    = 7882,  -- They don't let raw recruits into the chateau, but no matter! I'll complete so many missions they'll make me a certified adventurer in no time!
        BUT_FIRST_I_LL_WARM_UP_ON_A                                             = 7883,  -- But first, I'll warm up on a few of those worms outside the city gates! You have to walk before you can fly, my friend.
        A_MAGIC_SHOP_OH_IT_S_RIGHT_NEAR                                         = 7884,  -- A magic shop? Oh, it's right near here. I'll go check it out sometime.
        A_PICKPOCKET_WHEW_MY_WALLET_S_SAFE_IT                                   = 7885,  -- A pickpocket!? Whew, my wallet's safe. It takes money to be an adventurer!
        I_VE_TOLD_FONTOUMANT_SO_ALL_YOU_HAVE                                    = 7886,  -- I've told Fontoumant, so all you have to do is deliver the goods to Avandale as...
        HEY_THERE_RE_SOME_THINGS_BEST_LEFT_UNHEARD                              = 7887,  -- Hey! There're some things best left unheard, stranger. I trust you'll be leaving... Now!
        COME_ON_MAN_I_THINK_WE_RE_A                                             = 7888,  -- Come on, man, I think we're a little over our heads here! Someone big over in Jeuno gave that to commemorate...
        H_HEY_WHO_ARE_YOU_I_DON_T                                               = 7889,  -- H-hey! Who are you? I don't know what you heard, but this is Brugaire Consortium business! Top secret. Get lost.
        HEY_I_MAY_BE_A_CHILD_BUT_I                                              = 7890,  -- Hey! I may be a child, but I am the captain of the Royal Knights Youth Division!
        MY_TROOPS_WELL_IT_S_JUST_ME_AND                                         = 7891,  -- My troops...well, it's just me and my brother, but Orcs shiver at our name! It's true!
        HEY_SALUTE_WHEN_YOU_SPEAK_TO_ME_I                                       = 7892,  -- Hey! Salute when you speak to me! I am second captain of the Royal Knights Youth Division! Don't make me use my nirvana slash on you!
        MAYBE_WE_COULD_USE_YOU_YOU_D_BE                                         = 7893,  -- Maybe we could use you. You'd be just a private...but there is plenty of opportunity for advancement.
        MY_GRANDPA_ALWAYS_SAID_THAT_ONLY_A_THIEF                                = 7894,  -- My grandpa always said that only a thief would take other people's things! If I find that pickpocket... Wham! Wham!
        MY_GRANDPA_ALWAYS_SAID_THAT_THE_ONLY_STUFF                              = 7895,  -- My grandpa always said that the only stuff thieves take are other people's things! If I find that pickpocket, he's chocobo-feed!
        HMPH_A_NEW_RECRUIT_ARE_YOU_LET_ME                                       = 7896,  -- Hmph. A new recruit, are you? Let me give you some advice. There's Orcs outside our walls, more now than ever.
        BEST_NOT_TO_FACE_THEM_BEFORE_YOU_RE                                     = 7897,  -- Best not to face them before you're ready. They're known to attack without warning... Nasty things!
        HEH_FIGHTING_IS_GOOD_BUT_DISCRETION_IS_THE                              = 7898,  -- Heh. Fighting is good, but discretion is the better part of valor! Run back to the gates if you need to.
        THAT_S_CALLED_A_STRATEGIC_RETREAT_THAT_IS                               = 7899,  -- That's called a strategic retreat, that is!
        YEAH_A_TRADEGIC_STRETREAT                                               = 7900,  -- Yeah, a tradegic stretreat!
        I_LL_NEVER_FORGET_THE_GREAT_WAR_OF                                      = 7901,  -- I'll never forget the Great War of twenty years ago. The kindred of the Shadow Lord... So many lives lost... My sons... Oh, my sons!
        I_LL_NOT_LET_IT_HAPPEN_AGAIN_NOT                                        = 7902,  -- I'll not let it happen again! Not while blood still flows through my veins!
        EVERY_MORNING_I_PRAY_TO_ALTANA_PLEASE_I                                 = 7903,  -- Every morning I pray to Altana. Please, I say, please let these days of peace go on, till that day when we can all laugh and say, Life is grand...life is beautiful!
        IT_SEEMS_EVERYONE_IS_WORRIED_ABOUT_THE_ORCS                             = 7904,  -- It seems everyone is worried about the Orcs these days. Something's going on, that's for certain!
        IT_S_ABOUT_TIME_WE_MARCHED_ON_THEIR                                     = 7905,  -- It's about time we marched on their camps, I say. We've put up with those Orcs long enough! We Elvaan must put them back in their place.
        I_HEARD_THE_ORCISH_CAMP_IN_WEST_RONFAURE                                = 7906,  -- I heard the Orcish camp in West Ronfaure is called Ghelsba. There are so many of them these days!
        AND_I_VE_HEARD_THEY_KIDNAP_PEOPLE_IT                                    = 7907,  -- And I've heard they kidnap people! It's horrible, just horrible.
        THIS_IS_THE_FIRST_I_VE_HEARD_OF                                         = 7908,  -- This is the first I've heard of a magic shop here in San d'Oria. Such arts have never been popular in the Kingdom.
        I_AM_MAUNADOLACE_OF_THE_TEMPLE_KNIGHTS_ON                               = 7909,  -- I am Maunadolace of the Temple Knights, on orders from the prince to watch the auction house. I would love to chat, but I'm on duty.
        A_FINE_CHOCOBO_IS_SHE_NOT_MY_TRIED                                      = 7910,  -- A fine chocobo, is she not? My tried and true companion, mine since she was but a chick.
        ADMITTEDLY_I_D_RATHER_BE_OUT_IN_THE                                     = 7911,  -- Admittedly, I'd rather be out in the field, doing battle with fiends, not standing here monitoring...commerce.
