        ME_NAME_S_GALLIJAUX_AND_I_D_TAKE                                        = 8151,  -- Me name's Gallijaux, and I'd take fishing over food and drink any day. This here's my little brother, Joulet. He's a bit of an angler, too.
        TRUTH_BE_TOLD_THAT_S_A_MATTER_OF                                        = 8152,  -- Truth be told, that's a matter of great contention between us. We've competed to see who's the better fisherman before, but could never agree on the results, you see.
