        I_KNEW_YOU_WERE_THE_TYPE_THAT_S                                         = 8155,  -- I knew you were the type! That's great. Now, I want you to bring me either % or %. Simple, eh?
        I_WON_T_ASK_HOW_YOU_GET_THEM                                            = 8156,  -- I won't ask how you get them, just bring them to me--the more the merrier, eh? And don't you worry, I always put me gil where me mouth is.
