        HOW_S_IT_GOING_WITH_YOU_I_VE                                            = 8158,  -- How's it going with you? I've got # [carp/carps] now--don't let me down!
        AH_LOOK_AT_WHAT_YOU_VE_BROUGHT_ME                                       = 8159,  -- Ah, look at what you've brought me. This'll do fine, it will. Bring more!
        HEY_HEY_I_APPRECIATE_YOUR_GENEROSITY_BUT_I                              = 8160,  -- Hey, hey... I appreciate your generosity, but I certainly didn't ask for nothing like this!
        WHAT_S_THIS_YOU_RE_HELPING_ME_BROTHER                                   = 8161,  -- What's this? You're helping me brother, are you? Be gone with you, then! Out of my sight!
        WELL_NOW_IT_SEEMS_THAT_YOU_VE_BROUGHT                                   = 8162,  -- Well now, it seems that you've brought me more than 10,000 carps! That's worth a reward to certify your accomplishment, methinks! You keep up the good work.
        GOOD_DAY_I_AM_JOULET_AND_GALLIJAUX_IS                                   = 8163,  -- Good day. I am Joulet, and Gallijaux is my elder brother. Our mother likes to say we were born with fishing rods in our hands.
        WE_VE_ALWAYS_WONDERED_WHO_WAS_THE_BETTER                                = 8164,  -- We've always wondered who was the better angler...but never could agree on the results of our contests, no matter how many times we tried.
        SO_WE_HAD_THE_IDEA_TO_MAKE_SOME                                         = 8165,  -- So we had the idea to make some friends, and invite them to fish, too, then compare who found the better fisherman. Might you be willing to help me out?
        HELP_JOULET_HELP_OUT_REFUSE                                             = 8166,  -- Help Joulet? Help out. Refuse.
        INDEED_SPLENDID_THEN_LISTEN_THE_TWO_KINDS_OF                            = 8167,  -- Indeed? Splendid! Then listen--the two kinds of fish I want you to bring me are % and %. That shouldn't be too hard, should it?
