        YOU_LL_BE_ECSTATIC_TO_KNOW_THAT_YOU                                     = 8174,  -- You'll be ecstatic to know that you've brought me more than 10,000 carps! I'd like to give you these tokens of my tremendous appreciation. Keep up the good work!
