        EVER_SINCE_THE_ORNAMENTS_WENT_UP_I_VE                                   = 8638,  -- Ever since the ornaments went up, I've been swamped with orders for new ones. I can't blame them, though. I mean, once you've seen the best, how can you put up with anything less? Am I right?
        HOWEVER_WITH_ALL_THIS_WORK_I_VE_HARDLY                                  = 8639,  -- However, with all this work, I've hardly had any time to live the celebrity lifestyle. To tell you the truth, I barely have the time to fetch my new shipments of supplies! Hey, you look like you've got some spare time on your hands. What do you say? Help out a rising superstar on his path to glory?
