        OH_IT_S_YOU_I_COULDN_T_WAIT                                             = 8647,  -- Oh, it's you. I couldn't wait any longer for you to bring back those supplies, so I used something else in their place. Now, the next shipment I need you to bring me is from the moogle in front of the Northern San d'Oria residential area. What, you didn't think you were done, did you?
