        THE_MOOGLE_WITH_MY_SUPPLIES_IS_IN_FRONT                                 = 8649,  -- The moogle with my supplies is in front of the Northern San d'Oria residential area.
        SIGH_I_KNOW_THEY_SAY_THAT_IN_LIFE                                       = 8650,  -- <Sigh> I know they say that in life you should stop and smell the roses, but none of those guys had orders to fill! Now, I'm going to give you one more chance. Hurry down to the Southern San d'Oria residential area and pick up my materials from the market moogle.
