        WHO_WOULD_DREAM_THAT_EITHER_OF_US_HAD                                   = 8696,  -- Who would dream that either of us had even traveled beyond the borders of San d'Oria? Do they believe we are like the Tavnazians of old and maintain trading partners in the Near East?
        I_HEAR_THE_TOWN_OF_AL_ZAHBI_A                                           = 8697,  -- I hear the town of Al Zahbi, a strategic location in the west of Aht Urhgan, often finds itself surrounded by invading beastman forces... What feeble defenses they must have in the Near East.
        THIS_IS_WHAT_COMES_OF_A_NATION_THAT                                     = 8698,  -- This is what comes of a nation that does not embrace the path of chivalry. Our heroic knights would make short work of any beastman horde, no matter their number! Long live King Destin!
        HMPH_THINKING_OF_BECOMING_A_MERCENARY_ARE_YOU                           = 8699,  -- Hmph, thinking of becoming a mercenary, are you? Let me give you some advice: The beastmen of the Near East are far more savage than the fiends of Ronfaure.
