        THAT_BADGE_IT_IS_AS_IF_THE_TERRIBLE                                     = 8705,  -- That badge... It is as if the terrible events of twenty years past have returned to haunt us...
        YES_THE_NATION_THEY_SPEAK_OF_LIES_FAR                                   = 8706,  -- Yes, the nation they speak of lies far away, yet I feel the seed of fear blossom in my heart. War is like a raging fire that leaps from country to country, consuming all in its path...
