        WHILE_FREE_RUNS_USUALLY_HAVE_NO_SPECIFIC_OBJECTIVES                     = 10289,  -- While free runs usually have no specific objectives, the higher your chocobo places, the better the prize you will receive. We suggest you use these races to improve your skills before embarking on the more difficult official races.
