        WELCOME_LADIES_AND_GENTLEMEN_IT_S_TIME_FOR                              = 10770,  -- Welcome, ladies and gentlemen! It's time for another action-packed chocobo race! I'll be your commentator, Goccilo.
        OUR_SPECIAL_GUESTS_TODAY_ARE_EVERYBODY_S_FAVORITE                       = 10771,  -- Our special guests today are everybody's favorite disgruntled chick, Sakura...
        AND_HER_FAITHFUL_SERVANT_TRANSLATOR_MARKOVICH                           = 10772,  -- ...and her faithful servant/translator, Markovich.
        GOOD_DAY_FOL                                                            = 10773,  -- Good day, fol--
        S_I                                                                     = 10774,  -- s%I
        SAKURA_SAYS_THAT_SHE_LOVES_YOU_ALL_FROM                                 = 10775,  -- Sakura says that she loves you all from the bottom of her tiny heart.
        ALRIGHTY_THEN_OUR_NEXT_RACE_FEATURES_OF_VANA                            = 10776,  -- Alrighty then, our next race features # of Vana'diel's top chocobos. Let us start off by introducing the birds and their jockeys.
        FIRST_WE_HAVE_WHO_WILL_BE_RIDDEN_BY                                     = 10777,  -- First we have %, who will be ridden by [the ace of the chase, Ignazio/three-time chocobo racing alltar, Eudocia/the bloody emperor, Roinolier/the empress of speed, Maurette/Lami-Baami Suave Esquire III/the red rose of racing, Sosopapa/CRA legend, Khowa Mathgalhi/rising CRA star, Bayansh].
        S_S_I                                                                   = 10778,  -- s%s%I
        SHE_SAYS_WHEN_THE_ACE_MAKES_CHASE_THERE                                 = 10779,  -- She says, When the ace makes chase, there's not a bird in Vana'diel who can keep pace.
        SHE_SAYS_AND_YOU_CAN_BET_THE_CHOCOBO                                    = 10780,  -- She says, And you can bet the chocobo farm that this year it'll be 'four-time' alltar!
        SHE_SAYS_THIS_JOCKEY_DOESN_T_GET_HIS                                    = 10781,  -- She says, This jockey doesn't get his name because he yields to through traffic, if you know what I mean.
        SHE_SAYS_THERE_ISN_T_A_JOCKEY_IN                                        = 10782,  -- She says, There isn't a jockey in Vana'diel who loves her steed more than the empress of speed.
        SHE_SAYS_THIS_HEART_THROB_TREATS_HIS_MOUNTS                             = 10783,  -- She says, This heart-throb treats his mounts like he treats his women--with an unparalleled sense of grace, a sixth sense, you could say.
        SHE_SAYS_SOSOPAPA_HAS_GOT_THE_MOVES_TO                                  = 10784,  -- She says, Sosopapa has got the moves to make even the stiffest of necks turn.
        SHE_SAYS_THIS_FORMER_RACING_CHAMPION_HAS_DECIDED                        = 10785,  -- She says, This former racing champion has decided to temporarily come out of retirement (again) for what will be her final race.
        SHE_SAYS_THIS_NATURAL_WASN_T_A_BORN                                     = 10786,  -- She says, This natural wasn't a born natural, but was born with natural ability that naturally transformed him into what we often call a 'natural.'
        NEXT_WE_HAVE_BEING_RIDDEN_BY                                            = 10787,  -- Next we have [Pure Beauty/Ambitious Impact/Young Typhoon], being ridden by [the chocogirl next door, Hazina/dark chocostalker, Pikanza/self-proclaimed chocogeek, Qunbubu].
        SAKURA_SAYS_DON_T_BE_FOOLED_BY_THE                                      = 10788,  -- Sakura says, Don't be fooled by the innocent smile--this girl will rip your chocobo's gizzard out and eat it for a late breakfast or early lunch!
        SAKURA_SAYS_THIS_GALKA_S_UNRELENTING_LOVE_FOR                           = 10789,  -- Sakura says, This Galka's unrelenting love for all things chocobo makes him a dangerous opponent on the track.
        SAKURA_SAYS_THOUSANDS_OF_HOURS_OF_CHOCORESEARCH_HAVE                    = 10790,  -- Sakura says, Thousands of hours of chocoresearch have sharpened the mind of this jolly jockey into a pointy stick, ready to poke and prod anyone who dares stand in her way.
        OUR_NEXT_CHOCOBO_IS_RIDDEN_BY                                           = 10791,  -- Our next chocobo is [Shining Lady/Moon Night/Jet Fire], ridden by [Chanaille, a.k.a. Dances With Chocobos/the chocowhisperer, Sah Zhaowam/Sakura's number one fan, Chamu-Pashamu].
        SAKURA_SAYS_AIN_T_NO_ONE_KNOWS_A                                        = 10792,  -- Sakura says, Ain't no one knows a chocobo's heart like this here lil' lady.
        SAKURA_SAYS_SHE_HAS_A_GOOD_GRASP_OF                                     = 10793,  -- Sakura says, She has a good grasp of our vocabulary, but her pronunciation, especially her gutturals and fricatives, need a little work.
        S_T                                                                     = 10794,  -- s%`t
        SAKURA_SAYS_SHE_KNOWS_WHO_SHE_LL_BE                                     = 10795,  -- Sakura says she knows who she'll be rooting for this race...
        THE_NEXT_CONTESTANT_IS_JOCKEYED_BY                                      = 10796,  -- The next contestant is [Invincible Ace/Gold Queen/Million Spirit], jockeyed by [chocobo reincarnate, Vieuballideme/hyper breeder, Graciela/20-year racing veteran, Mayza-Hapurza].
        SHE_SAYS_THAT_SIMPLY_SMELLING_LIKE_A_CHOCOBO                            = 10797,  -- She says that simply smelling like a chocobo doesn't make one a chocobo.
        SHE_SAYS_THAT_BREEDING_CHOCOBOS_IS_LIKE_STOCKING                        = 10798,  -- She says that breeding chocobos is like stocking a warehouse with 10,000 opo-opos and 10,000 typewriters--you are bound to stumble across a masterpiece sooner or later.
        SHE_SAYS_THAT_THIS_TARUTARU_HAS_BEEN_PRACTICING                         = 10799,  -- She says that this Tarutaru has been practicing the choquestrian arts since he was only two years old.
        AND_THAT_S_OUR_LINEUP_PERHAPS_IT_IS                                     = 10800,  -- And that's our lineup. Perhaps it is just me, but I have a feeling that today's match up will go down in the annals of racing history.
        AND_HERE_S_TODAY_S_LINEUP_WHAT_EXCITEMENT                               = 10801,  -- And here's today's lineup. What excitement lies in store for all our faithful chocofans listening on the CRA linkshell channel?
        THE_CONTESTANTS_HAVE_ARRIVED_AT_THE_STARTING_LINE                       = 10802,  -- The contestants have arrived at the starting line, and the race will begin shortly.
        WELCOME_LADIES_AND_GENTLEMEN_TO_ANOTHER_ROUND_OF                        = 10803,  -- Welcome, ladies and gentlemen to another round of awe-inspiring head-to-head chocobo racing! I am Goccilo, your master of ceremonies.
        AND_JOINING_US_TODAY_ARE_THE_COMMENTATING_DUO                           = 10804,  -- And joining us today are the commentating duo which require no introduction, the equally adroit and adorable Sakura...
