        THE_RESISTANCE_IS_CURRENTLY_SUFFERING_A_MATERIALS_SHORTAGE              = 11627,  -- The resistance is currently suffering a materials shortage. Those wishing to participating in replenishment and upgrading operations should return at a later time.
